OL,5, Mortgage deals are typically on offer  
OL,6, for just 15 days before being pulled,  
OL,7, despite homeowners and buyers having   
OL,8, the widest choice for 16 years.        
OL,10,FThis is the shortest shelf-life in six 
OL,11,Fmonths, according to financial         
OL,12,Finformation service Moneyfacts.        
OL,14,FAs a result, people have little time to
OL,15,Fdecide when rates are volatile.        
OL,17,FOne adviser said the situation was     
OL,18,Fadding extra stress to a huge financial
OL,19,Fcommitment and making customers feel   
OL,20,Fpressured to make a decision quickly.  
